SELECT "p"."project_id",ROUND(AVG("e"."experience_years"), 2) AS "average_years" FROM "Project" AS "p" JOIN "Employee" AS "e" ON "p"."employee_id"="e"."employee_id" GROUP BY "p"."project_id"
SELECT "project_id",ROUND(AVG("experience_years"), 2) AS "average_years" FROM "Project" LEFT JOIN "Employee" USING ("employee_id") GROUP BY "project_id"
